{"tid":924452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【查稅黑名單】17位藝人被大陸稅局召見 傳鄧超夫婦需補2.5億稅款","createTime":"2018-12-02T06:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T07:47:56.000Z","uid":224066,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6512eb00c09be749f2c1e775f0f6995d4c2de16d","tid":924452,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5X7Mhn_LV8fPGk_z44AYFw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/c8cd4904bdc227e8fc0f87215e0cff89\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5X7Mhn_LV8fPGk_z44AYFw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjQwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fc8cd4904bdc227e8fc0f87215e0cff89&h=ce4dda62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸稅務局要嚴查影視界中人逃稅問題，范冰冰首先被稅局開刀要罰近10億港元），而其他藝人陸續被當局召去問話，有消息指呢3日內已約見咗17位藝人，並要佢哋喺12月15日限期前自行補稅，雖未公開約談名單，<span style=\"color: red;\">但目前微博瘋傳鄧超孫儷夫婦、楊穎（Angelababy）及老公黃曉明、周迅、楊冪、趙薇、吳奇隆、趙麗穎、陳喬恩、黃渤、徐崢、吳京、吳秀波、霍建華等都在名單內，</span>聽講呢班藝人有唔少需要補稅達2億人民幣（逾2.24億港元）以上，單係鄧超夫婦就要補2.5億人民幣（約2.81億港元）稅款。<br />\n<br />\n逃稅事件已鬧得滿城風雨，稅務局呢輪係咁針對影視業進行查稅清算，如果呢班藝人冇喺限定期完成補稅，相信都幾麻煩。有啲藝人可能唔夠現金，o依家都要將一啲物業放手，盡快籌夠錢嚟補稅。另外，編劇、造型師、導演同攝影師等幕後工作人員近幾年都搵唔少，稅務局又點放過佢哋唔查？"},{"pid":"c1a94e827a8296b8e9158bfc19decb1b308add8c","tid":924452,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"至美的活祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098c408be1f770e1ddc36f26128da1d8049e45e1","tid":924452,"uid":38904,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"交稅, 一點都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24962287e5c6fc815df72d022d7ad4eddc2baacb","tid":924452,"uid":20058,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,